{"id": "1242342773667926036", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "打的好，笑死", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T05:06:38.855000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["232848201500065792"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242291869501755432", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242342873265868850", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:proud2:1236950158500040764>", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T05:07:02.601000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242360277039714324", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "那你的隊伍構築一定很有意思，或者有亮點……不過太巧了，隔幾局又遇到\n有時候是會卡住，有一次我打榜二的西維斯特開局也卡了，動不了，重連已經輸掉出來了", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:16:11.984000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["372020544494764043"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242101243950665728", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242361023139414097", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "看你喜歡什麼隊伍，現在比較流行的有水母希洛隊、毒隊、爆發隊，還有炒飯愛用的流血隊，也有驅散隊，可以都嘗試一下再決定", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:19:09.868000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["593627944979660800"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242266675299225621", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242361365432238110", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "後面的爆發隊指的是用利茲+環娜打黎明/翠星，另外還有麻痺隊和羅坦隊", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:20:31.477000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242361537520341113", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "也有人打凱+水母的重創反擊和鯊的回血", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:21:12.506000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242362805173223477", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "好操作的話，我覺得流血隊很順手……這之前用最多的是爆發隊，神父+溫柯爾+環娜+利茲，利茲比較推薦巨人之刃（不過我沒有），同理鯊也適合這個，命輪最推薦資訊就是生命，由於這隊沒治療可以帶饕餮寓言/騎士之心加生存，或帶迷失的道路專注輸出", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:26:14.738000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:27:27.244000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242362997830189066", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "每個人都有自己的習慣吧，甚至遇到過對面只剩一個伽倫輸出翻盤，但我玩不來伽倫，水母希洛和毒隊也不順手", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:27:00.671000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242363279645343754", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "女王之劍寫了水母希洛隊的攻略，攻略板塊裡應該能看到", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:28:07.861000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242364246818553997", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "要用羅坦來打擊的話就帶堅韌意志（5費，有點貴）和狂亂（打擊+15狂氣），但遇見麻痺隊或被纏繞容易劣勢，治療推薦能驅散的朵爾，輔助推薦汀克特/諾締拉，驅散或強化+給予打擊", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:31:58.453000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242364605783736390", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我看女王劍也開始玩流血了", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:33:24.037000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242364729251598368", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "我最近再試牌，分數那是無止境的噴", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:33:53.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242365039453667460", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "感覺重創隊有點好玩，但是真的太過不穩定，要各種控", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:35:07.432000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242365489565532230", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "女王之劍好像換不同的隊伍玩，之前遇見過毒隊，昨晚玩流血遇見了魔術師+朵爾+尤烏，魔法師過牌，朵爾快樂魔法秀過牌，主打一個牌庫隨便翻", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:36:54.747000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242365717072973855", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "嗯……是的，而且凱刻斯應該怕反擊被驅散", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:37:48.989000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242365725474164808", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛才也是遇到這組", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:37:50.992000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242365938754388061", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "剛才我也有打，請問你的id是……？說不定我們也遇見過", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:38:41.842000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242365983348232242", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "凱刻斯怕麻痺，也怕對面菲因特搶狀態", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:38:52.474000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242366126348828783", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "貓頭鷹小七，你是至高的話我們其實碰到不少次", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:39:26.568000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1241965800793837578"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242365938754388061", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242366262202601492", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "對，昨晚也碰到了，我還疑惑你的分原來很高怎麼掉那麼多", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:39:58.958000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242366512933634108", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "想說之前掉到2200了，就乾脆試試其它牌玩看看，然後再把自己玩掉1000分", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:40:58.737000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242366536166015047", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "昨晚我在試驗新搞的隊，因為昨晚總撞毒隊搞了個驅散隊，然後我們兩個魔術師絲血對戰", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:41:04.276000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242366869617377361", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 19, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "試牌組就是很容易掉……上賽季最後我試牌組掉了1800分", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:42:23.777000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["274888866941501442"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1242366512933634108", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242366902387609650", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前玩起來覺得有趣是重創隊，但是剋星太多，主動權又偏低", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:42:31.590000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242367263160533063", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "對，凱刻斯打反擊，但又沒嘲諷，我遇見的大多數是最後剩一兩個角色凱刻斯翻盤", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:43:57.605000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242367473173659668", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "1241965800793837578", "author_name": "_destreza_", "author_bot": false, "content": "要想有趣的話我推薦一個，艾爾瓦放最後帶至為珍貴的藏品，前面放水母+伽倫+諾締拉，很快樂，不過分會一直掉", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:44:47.676000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242368120186863677", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "妥的，下次試試，感謝", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:47:21.936000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1242368280975638590", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "274888866941501442", "author_name": "wuboying.", "author_bot": false, "content": "重創隊感覺缺那種單點主力", "timestamp": "2024-05-21T06:48:00.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
